# SuperSimple2DKit
A simple kit meant to help jump start the creation of your 2D Unity game!

Creator: Thomas Brush
Install & Usage Instructions: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-mwooH1Bro
Unity Version: 2020.3.19f1
